# WPEngine Site Maintainence
1. Refer to Environment Management for details about the state of the environment
2. Copy Productions to a free environment
3. Run Environment Updates
4. Run Pagespeed
5. Run visual QA
6. Record findings
7. Open a changelog ticket in the respective site's repo project on github as a new ticket, using the description outline below and filing in "Resources/Reference Links" to include the pastel link, development environment link, and fill in the overview with quick summary of findings ( to be finalized by the lead ).
8. Notify lead(s). Include a time estimation of work and timliness of work (is something broken before the update)?
9. Assign ticket to lead for `scoping`

## Ticket Description Structure

```
## Overview

## Development Tasks

## Resources/Reference Links

## Completion Validation

```
